<i>noun</i>: 경직성 [경직썽], 경직 [경직] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>경직성 [경직썽]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stiffness</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 몸의 일부가 굳어서 뻣뻣해지는 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality of a body or body part becoming stiff and rigid.</dd><br>
<dd>2. rigidity; inflexibility</dd><br>
<dd>생각, 행동, 분위기 등이 융통성이 없고 엄격한 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality of becoming inflexible and strict in one's ideas, behavior, attitudes, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>경직 [경직]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stiffness; being stiff</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 몸의 일부가 굳어서 뻣뻣하게 됨.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which the body or a part of it becomes stiff and rigid.</dd><br>
<dd>2. rigidity; inflexibility</dd><br>
<dd>생각, 행동, 분위기 등이 융통성이 없고 엄격함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one's idea, behavior, atmosphere, etc., become inflexible and strict.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>